description: This charming and stylish villa with a usable area of 463 m² is situated on a domain of 9,981 m² and offers an open and green view. The house, built in 1985, was finished with quality and robust materials. This property lends itself ideally to the practice of a liberal profession, thanks to the present parking spaces, separate entrance and consultation room. Horse lovers are also welcome here, thanks to the stables and adjacent meadows. Privacy guaranteed thanks to its location in a dead-end street, orientation of the house and the landscaped garden as a green buffer. We enter the farmhouse through the entrance hall with separate guest toilet and access to a desk/consultation room. The living space is open, bright and classy and fully finished with fully fledged materials. Cozy dining with the family, relaxing by the wood fire and overlooking the surrounding greenery. The kitchen was renovated in 2012 and offers modern living comfort. Then there is the utility room, with connections, access to the basement and storage room. The ground floor is completed with a second separate toilet and the double garage, closed by automatic tilt doors. The first floor houses a total of 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The master has an en-suite bathroom (bath, shower, double sink, toilet). The second bathroom is located on the landing and also has a double washbasin, shower and bath. Large plus is the multipurpose, still to be decorated free space, with access to the attic. Extra living space easy to create if desired! The property, consisting of 3 plots, includes a paddock for horses, an outbuilding with stables, south facing terrace and landscaped green areas. Privacy, relaxation and enjoyment guaranteed.Urban.
